<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ElTaksi - Haydovchi Kirish</title>
    <style>
        :root { --midnight: #0b1120; --gold: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #f59e0b 100%); --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }

        body {
            background: var(--midnight);
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.05) 0%, transparent 20%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 90% 80%, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.05) 0%, transparent 20%);
            height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white;
        }

        .login-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            width: 90%; max-width: 380px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .logo-icon {
            font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 10px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3));
        }

        h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .info-text { font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.5; margin-bottom: 25px; line-height: 1.4; }
        
        .contact-box {
            background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.07);
            padding: 12px; border-radius: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px;
            border: 1px dashed rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);
        }
        .contact-box a { color: #fbbf24; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; }

        .input-group { position: relative; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        
        input {
            width: 100%; padding: 15px 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 18px; color: white; font-size: 0.95rem;
            outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        input:focus { border-color: #fbbf24; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); }

        .login-btn {
            width: 100%; padding: 16px; border-radius: 18px; border: none;
            background: var(--gold); color: #0b1120;
            font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease; margin-top: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        }

        .login-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 15px 20px -3px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4); opacity: 0.9; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="login-card">
        <div class="logo-icon">🚕</div>
        <h2>Xush kelibsiz</h2>
        <p class="info-text">Kirish uchun ofis tomonidan berilgan login va parolni kiriting.</p>

        <div class="contact-box">
            <a href="tel:+998901234567">Ofis bilan bog'lanish</a>
        </div>

        <form action="/driver-login" method="POST">
            <div class="input-group">
                <input type="text" name="login" placeholder="Login" required>
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Parol" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="login-btn">TIZIMGA KIRISH</button>
        </form>
    </div>

</body>
</html>